				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${70}{\%}$$\end{document}. In case the TE system is used to generate surplus electricity from the excess heat of a photovoltaic or solar thermal system, the overall efficiency increases by 34%\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
